1040
00:56:01,754 --> 00:56:04,007
Yes, she's a person.

1041
00:56:04,090 --> 00:56:06,885
A person who does things like this
to young high school girls.

1042
00:56:06,968 --> 00:56:09,137
The public is entitled to know.

1043
00:56:10,430 --> 00:56:12,640
Enough is enough, you crazy bitches!

1044
00:56:14,642 --> 00:56:17,312
