1072
00:57:37,892 --> 00:57:40,228
How many people does it take?
Is there a number?

1073
00:57:40,311 --> 00:57:42,146
The public is
an unspecified number of people.

1074
00:57:42,230 --> 00:57:44,357
Are you going to
keep quibbling over words?

1075
00:57:44,440 --> 00:57:47,402
