1092
00:58:30,653 --> 00:58:33,990
Still, have you seen the comments?
Have you read what they say?

1093
00:58:34,073 --> 00:58:35,742
Yes. Comments like these, right?

1094
00:58:39,287 --> 00:58:40,204
Goodness.

1095
00:58:41,789 --> 00:58:43,750
"Didn't she fix her whole face?"

1096
00:58:43,833 --> 00:58:45,293
"How blessed she is."

1097
00:58:45,376 --> 00:58:47,837
"The blessing of Korean doctors."

1098
00:58:47,920 --> 00:58:50,006
She's the most overrated these days.

1099
00:58:50,590 --> 00:58:52,383
She pretended to be pretty and kind.

1100
00:58:52,467 --> 00:58:54,427
Admit you got plastic surgery first.

1101
00:58:54,510 --> 00:58:57,847
"Did she make all those donations
to evade taxes?"

1102
00:58:59,641 --> 00:59:03,728
I wonder how many people there are

1103
00:59:04,312 --> 00:59:06,022
who leave comments like these.

1104
00:59:06,606 --> 00:59:10,318
Are they really the only ones
who make up the public?

1105
00:59:10,943 --> 00:59:14,405
There are people
who don't even know Elijah at all.

1106
00:59:14,489 --> 00:59:17,450
There are those
who love her music quietly.

1107
00:59:17,533 --> 00:59:21,204
There are many
who frown upon comments like these.

1108
00:59:21,704 --> 00:59:26,542
Ms. Ma, did you at least take
a public survey from every citizen?

1109
00:59:26,626 --> 00:59:28,461
On what premises

1110
00:59:28,544 --> 00:59:30,963
