to say that it hurts.

1155
01:02:08,162 --> 01:02:09,413
Think about it.

1156
01:02:10,248 --> 01:02:13,543
How many times have we lost

1157
01:02:14,836 --> 01:02:16,712
those lonely and vulnerable stars

1158
01:02:18,798 --> 01:02:20,424
that shined…

1159
01:02:22,593 --> 01:02:24,554
so brightly?

1160
01:02:28,391 --> 01:02:32,144
Does the price for popularity
have to be that cruel?

1161
01:02:40,111 --> 01:02:40,945
Ms. Ma.

1162
01:02:42,572 --> 01:02:44,407
You must take responsibility now

1163
01:02:44,490 --> 01:02:47,493
